snippet.title: Super Meat Boy Forever: PAX West Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Dr. Fetus is being a jerk again (as he does), but this time he’s kidnapped Meat Boy and Bandage Girl’s adorable little baby girl, named Nugget! Super Meat Boy Forever is coming to Nintendo Switch in 2018!

Learn more about Super Meat Boy Forever for Nintendo Switch! https://goo.gl/7eyHU6
